Check this question for more information: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/15507997/how-to-prevent-gson-from-expressing-integers-as-floats

I suggest you to use [Jackson Mapper][1]. Jackson distinguish between type even if you are parsing to an Object:

 - `&quot;2&quot;` as `Integer`
